#ad Surviving on protein bars and beer!
Wanted to review and share with you guys some of my favorite @imbuilt flavors while enjoying a  Kuri-Kuro Dark Chestnut Ale by the brewery Miyazaki Hideji Beer.
Give Built Bar a follow on Instagram and use my discount code thegirlwithbeer for $5 OFF 10 bar sample box.

node.text:
Making the best of the last days of summer.

🍻 @fourwindsbrewco Nectarous,  Dry hopped sour.

I don’t know why it took me so long to try this beer. It’s highly rated and has won “Beer of the year” in Canada 2016 and various silver and gold medals at the Canadian Brewing awards over the years. I always see people drinking this too but I finally gave it a shot, and damn it’s good! A very approachable Sour Ale that is not overly fruity or sour, you get notes of peach and nectarine from the esters versus added fruit. I think it’s a great beer for sour lovers but also a gateway beer for those who don’t usually reach for sours. 

#thegirlwithbeer

Can I squat you? 

Sooooo I squatted my followers and drank their favorite beer. That last one was a struggle but made it!!

280 lbs- Hazy Ipa - @superfluxbeer Double Infinity vic secret - Double hazy IPA
300 lbs barrel aged stout -espresso de medianoche @boquetebrewingcompany 

#explorepage #igreels #girlswhopowerlift @workforyourbeer @earnyourbooze #workforyourbeer #earnyourbooze #craftbeer #thegirlwithbeer #girlswholift

node.text:
As I sip my #FirstLaphroaig it takes me back to my time in Scotland; salt, smoke and whisky! 🥃 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿
 
Laphroaig 10 Year Old is complex, boasting notes of seaweed, a hint of sweetness and a lingering peatiness on the finish.
 
As you all know, I'm a beer lover but @laphroaig has shown me a whole new world. 

Are you familiar with Laphroaig? Would you #PassThePeat?

Share your #FirstLaphroaig experience with me below.

#PassThePeat
#OpinionsWelcome
#FirstLaphroaig
